A year after a series of tragic incidents that happened at “Fang and Friends Pizza Parlor” they have announced the reopening of its establishment. CEO Melchior Sepulveda said “It’s great to be back in working order again. Hopefully, we can learn from our previous mistakes, and kick our competition into the ground.”

After a 5 month in-depth investigation and numerous trails, the case has gone cold. To this day it is still unknown who or what caused the missing children incident at Fang and Friends Pizza Parlor.
